                  ṣaḥafe tǝʾǝzāz</roleName></persName>
                   during the time of 
                 
                  <persName ref="PRS2377Bakaffa"> <roleName type="title">ʾaṣe </roleName> Bakāffā</persName>. 
                  He continued to write the chronicle of 
                  <persName ref="PRS2377Bakaffa"><roleName type="title">ʾaṣe </roleName> Bakāffā</persName>
                  after the death of 
                  <persName ref="PRS8869Sinoda"><roleName type="title">ʾazzāž </roleName> 
                     Sinodā</persName>. He wrote the
                  last 14 chapters of the chronicle of 
                  <persName ref="PRS2377Bakaffa"> <roleName type="title">ʾaṣe </roleName> Bakāffā</persName>, 
                  recording events from mid-August 1726 to January 1727.</floruit>
              
